reviewText: The quality of this DVD has s the worst ever. The information is okay, but nothing great. I will put it in my next donation box.
Very informative on older Rome.  Saving fir a vacation there next year.  Lots of good tips in wrote down fir my visit.
Poorly filmed, colour is not good and several images are out of focus. I actually can't use this with students. There are so many DVDs out there that are so much better.
Poor photography and weak narrative, including a voice that should NOT be used to narrate anything: hard to hear, hard to understand, sing-songy. Disappointed in this DVD,
Great history of Rome, but didn't show what we thought it would....wanted more info on current Rome.
